%^RESET%^%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^Prestige Class
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Metamind:

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Requirements:
%^RESET%^ Level 40 Character
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^ %^RESET%^ Level 20 Psywarrior
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^ %^RESET%^ 20 Points Spent in the Academics Skill
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^ %^RESET%^ 20 Base Intelligence (before equipment modifiers)

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Class Feats:%^RESET%^
 %^RESET%^L1: mind partition
 %^RESET%^L4: mental fortress
 %^RESET%^L7: mind wave

Metaminds have mastered control over their minds, making them particularlyresilient, especially to attacks against their psyche. After countless hours spent honing their mental prowess, metaminds are able to ignore mindcontrolling effects used against them. The metamind is also able to project a portion of himself into the astral plane, granting the timelessbody power. A metamind is also so skilled with mental exercises that theygain a +2 to all academics and spellcraft checks.

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^See also: %^RESET%^feats, skills, spells, cast, prepare